00:15:39.330 --> 00:15:42.330
Dzīvnieku pīlings. Mecho-Gecko - pīlings

00:15:42.330 --> 00:15:45.330
kas ļauj tiem kāpt autonomi. Var doties pa plakanu virsmu

00:15:45.330 --> 00:15:48.330
